    </div>
    <div class="card">
        <div class="blog">
            <div class="header">
                <h3>Meta's AI Race</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="info">
                <p>Meta's preparation to lead in the AI race by hiring OpenAI's talent with a joining bonus of whopping
